\]

Оператор Лапласа:

\[
\Delta f=\frac{1}{a^{2}}(\operatorname{ch} \tau-\cos \sigma)^{2}\left(\frac{\partial^{2} f}{\partial \sigma^{2}}+\frac{\partial^{2} f}{\partial \tau^{2}}\right)+\frac{\partial^{2} f}{\partial z^{2}} .
\]

